How it ran and whistled! Yesthere are more of them.
I must get a dog. I won't go abroad again, after
whortleberries
,
without a dog.
I went to bed; but, half a dozen times, did I awake,
screaming with affright; and fancying that the creature
was chasing me yet, and chattering over my shoulder
just overtaking methat his boneless fingers, were
just touching meI could feel them mounting to my
