frightened than shewell done!
Down went the candleand we were left for a
moment
,
in absolute darkness. I attempted to find it;
and, in doing so, I encountered a soft handah,
heaven!ere I could withdraw itI felt the pressure
of a warm trembling mouth upon itI was strangely
