that her companion had company, popped in,
accidentally
upon us; though it snowed and blew, like vengeance;
and the houses were half a mile apartwithout her
bonnet. This, of course, excited some consideration;
and in me, for such is my nature, when I see women
behave like foolssome reproof. She liked me the
